Rico, flip six three hole. Got it? Hey, Rico?

174
00:11:29,632 --> 00:11:32,002
- 嘿! - 什么?
- Hey! - What?

175
00:11:32,092 --> 00:11:35,672
专心点 翻跳动作 懂吗?
You're drifting! Flip six, three hole, on one! Got it?

176
00:11:35,762 --> 00:11:39,052
- 尽管把球传给我 蒂丝 - 准备好了?
-Just throw me the ball, Diz. - Ready? Break!

177
00:11:59,162 --> 00:12:02,202
好! 走 走!
Yeah! Go, go, go!

178
00:12:04,332 --> 00:12:06,292
好!
All right!

179
00:12:09,462 --> 00:12:11,702
耶!
Yeah!

180
00:12:11,802 --> 00:12:14,252
得分了 比赛结束
He's in there. It's over.

181
00:12:30,402 --> 00:12:32,692
你一下子就长这么大了
Who said you could grow up so fast, huh?

182
00:12:32,782 --> 00:12:34,822
妈 别这样
Mom, don't get mushy.

183
00:12:36,782 --> 00:12:38,772
这是今天寄来的
This came for you today.

184
00:12:38,872 --> 00:12:40,742
是你要的吧?
I presume, at your request.

185
00:12:44,502 --> 00:12:46,622
我有很多朋友都要服役
A lot of my friends are doing Federal Service.

186
00:12:46,712 --> 00:12:49,162
你不是想报名入伍吧?
Well, you're not thinking of applying?

187
00:12:49,252 --> 00:12:51,292
你疯啦?
Have you lost your mind?

188
00:12:51,382 --> 00:12:54,582
我就算是要挨鞭刑也不准你去自毁前程
I'd rather take ten lashes in Public Square than see you ruin your life.

189
00:12:54,672 --> 00:12:56,922
这是志愿服役
It's a term of service.

190
00:12:57,012 --> 00:12:58,922
不是从军
It's not a career.

191
00:12:59,012 --> 00:13:01,132
我只想一个人出去...
I just want to get out on my own...

192
00:13:02,682 --> 00:13:05,092
见识一下银河系风光
see the galaxy for a couple years.

193
00:13:05,182 --> 00:13:07,592
强尼 当兵会死人的
Johnny, people get killed in the Federal Service.

194
00:13:07,692 --> 00:13:11,392
是谁把你说动的? 是那个老师 对吧?
Who gave you this idea? It's that teacher, isn't it?

195
00:13:11,482 --> 00:13:14,402
他叫什么? 你应该知道
What's his name? You know the one I'm talking about.

196
00:13:15,532 --> 00:13:18,612
- 瑞斯加科先生 - 瑞斯加科?
- Mr Rasczak. - Rasczak?

197
00:13:20,702 --> 00:13:22,942
这名字真可笑 法律应该...
Silly name. There should be a law against...

198
00:13:23,042 --> 00:13:25,192
禁止学校召募新兵
using a school as a recruiting station.

199
00:13:25,292 --> 00:13:29,662
瑞斯加科不会这么做
No, Rasczak doesn't do that at all.

200
00:13:29,752 --> 00:13:31,832
其实他反对学生从军
He sort of discourages you.

201
00:13:31,922 --> 00:13:33,712
那就好
Well, that's good.

202
00:13:33,802 --> 00:13:36,832
你得上哈佛 没什么好说的
'Cause you're going to Harvard, and that's the end of it.

203
00:13:36,922 --> 00:13:39,422
这是我的决定 不是你的
It's my decision, not yours.

204
00:13:39,512 --> 00:13:42,132
- 是这样吗? - 别吵了
- Oh, is that how it is, huh? - Wait, you two.

205
00:13:42,222 --> 00:13:45,672
我和你父亲要给你个惊喜
Uh, Dad and I have a surprise for you that will settle this.

206
00:13:45,772 --> 00:13:48,222
你猜得到吗?
Can you guess what it is?

207
00:13:48,312 --> 00:13:49,642
猜不到
No.

208
00:13:50,812 --> 00:13:52,522
你想见识银河系风光
You wanted to see the galaxy?

209
00:13:53,822 --> 00:13:56,822
到土星外环旅行如何?
How about a trip to the Outer Rings?

210
00:13:56,902 --> 00:13:59,822
西格玛海滩
Zegema Beach. Huh?

211
00:14:02,372 --> 00:14:03,942
我一直想去那儿
I've always wanted to go there.

212
00:14:04,032 --> 00:14:06,572
很好 就这么说定了
Good, good. Then it's all settled.

213
00:14:23,602 --> 00:14:25,922
别走开
Sure. Don't go away.

214
00:14:26,012 --> 00:14:27,892
我想找瑞斯加科先生
I'm just gonna go see Mr Rasczak.

215
00:14:29,982 --> 00:14:32,022
瑞哥 想跳舞吗?
Hey, Rico, do you want to dance?

216
00:14:32,102 --> 00:14:33,682
蒂丝 我答应卡门
Actually, Diz, I promised Carmen...

217
00:14:33,772 --> 00:14:35,732
真可惜 她不在
Aw, come on. Too bad for her if she's not around.

218
00:14:39,492 --> 00:14:42,242
过了今晚...
You know, it's sad. After tonight, most of us...

219
00:14:42,322 --> 00:14:44,202
我们恐怕不会再见面
probably won't see each other again.

220
00:14:47,832 --> 00:14:49,872
你要替巴西队打球吗?
So, you still gonna play for Rio?

221
00:14:51,922 --> 00:14:54,372
是呀 除非东京队要征召我
Yeah, looks like. Unless Tokyo lets me start.

222
00:14:54,462 --> 00:14:56,702
谁抢到你就走运
Well, anyone who gets you is lucky.

223
00:14:58,092 --> 00:15:00,762
我们怎么没成为一对?
Johnny, how come we never got together?

224
00:15:04,762 --> 00:15:06,722
我们不能只当朋友吗?
Can't we just be friends, Diz?

225
00:15:09,432 --> 00:15:10,812
好
Sure.

226
00:15:14,522 --> 00:15:16,432
- 谢谢 - 晚上好
- Thank you. - Good night.

227
00:15:16,522 --> 00:15:20,222
蒂丝 我想找瑞斯加科先生
Look, Diz, I want to talk to Mr Rasczak.

228
00:15:22,652 --> 00:15:25,062
你最好赶快去
Well, you better hurry up if you want to catch him.

229
00:15:25,162 --> 00:15:26,492
你对我最好
You're the best.

230
00:15:39,672 --> 00:15:41,252
瑞斯加科先生
Mr Rasczak!

231
00:15:41,342 --> 00:15:44,292
- 什么事? 瑞哥 - 我要谢谢你
- What is it, Rico? - I want to thank you.

232
00:15:44,382 --> 00:15:46,962
我最喜欢你的课
Your class was the best one I had this year.

233
00:15:47,052 --> 00:15:49,632
我只希望你能有所收获
Well, it's really not my job to please. I just hope you learned something.

234
00:15:49,722 --> 00:15:51,472
我想入伍
Well, I want to join up.

235
00:15:51,562 --> 00:15:53,472
我觉得我有成为公民的勇气
I think I got what it takes to be a citizen.

236
00:15:53,562 --> 00:15:55,932
很好 去试吧
Good for you. Go find out.

237
00:15:56,022 --> 00:15:57,932
这是我的决定我父母却反对
Well, my parents are against it.

238
00:15:58,022 --> 00:15:59,602
我知道这是我的选择
And I know it's my choice.

239
00:15:59,692 --> 00:16:01,482
我在想...
I was wondering...

240
00:16:01,572 --> 00:16:02,852
你若是我 你会怎么做?
what would you do if you were me?

241
00:16:04,032 --> 00:16:05,312
能决定自己的前程
Figuring things out for yourself...

242
00:16:05,412 --> 00:16:07,652
才是真正的自由
is the only freedom anyone really has.

243
00:16:07,742 --> 00:16:09,152
珍惜这自由
Use that freedom.

244
00:16:09,242 --> 00:16:11,452
自己决定吧
Make up your own mind, Rico.

245
00:16:33,232 --> 00:16:34,802
别乱讲
Don't exaggerate.

246
00:16:34,892 --> 00:16:37,892
是真的 你的眼睛好美
I'm serious. I think you have really beautiful eyes.

247
00:16:37,982 --> 00:16:39,812
- 你了解? - 强尼
- You know? -Johnny.

248
00:16:42,402 --> 00:16:44,642
这是山德
Uh, this is Zander.

249
00:16:44,742 --> 00:16:47,492
我们在球场上较过劲
Yeah, we know each other from the game.

250
00:16:47,572 --> 00:16:52,482
- 你不介意吧? - 不介意 我们赢了
- No hard feelings? - No, none at all. We won.

251
00:16:52,582 --> 00:16:56,332
来吧 卡门 最后一支舞
Come on, Carmen. It's the last dance.

252
00:16:56,422 --> 00:16:58,412
也许我在军校会见到你
Well, maybe I'll see you at the Academy.

253
00:16:58,502 --> 00:16:59,832
是啊 也许会吧
Yeah. Who knows?

254
00:17:02,092 --> 00:17:06,582
- 祝你好运 - 山德也要当飞行员
- Good luck. - Zander's going for pilot too.

255
00:17:08,092 --> 00:17:10,502
你们真是绝配 卡门
You two have so much in common.

256
00:17:10,602 --> 00:17:13,682
强尼·瑞哥 你在吃醋吗?
Johnny Rico, are you jealous?

257
00:17:13,772 --> 00:17:16,442
也许吧
Well, maybe.

258
00:17:16,522 --> 00:17:18,682
你不必吃醋
You don't have to be jealous.

259
00:17:23,032 --> 00:17:24,602
嗨 嗨...快分开 你们两个
Hey, hey, break it up, you two.

260
00:17:24,692 --> 00:17:27,182
要亲热就到别的地方
There's a place for that sort of thing.

261
00:17:30,202 --> 00:17:33,952
我考虑好了 我要入伍
I've been thinking, and I'm gonna do it, Carmen.

262
00:17:34,042 --> 00:17:35,912
我要加入联邦军队
I'm gonna go for Federal Service.

263
00:17:36,002 --> 00:17:38,292
太好了
That's great.

264
00:17:38,372 --> 00:17:41,292
我和卡尔明天登记 和我们一起去吧
Carl and I are signing up tomorrow. Come with us.

265
00:17:41,382 --> 00:17:42,712
我会的
I will.

266
00:17:48,552 --> 00:17:51,722
我父亲今晚不在家
My father's not home tonight.

267
00:18:12,162 --> 00:18:15,742
我了解从军的...
I do now, of my own free will...

268
00:18:15,832 --> 00:18:19,242
意义和义务
after having been duly advised and warned...

269
00:18:19,332 --> 00:18:22,582
这一切完全出于自愿
of the meaning and consequences of this oath...

270
00:18:22,672 --> 00:18:24,912
我至少
enrol in the Federal Service...

271
00:18:25,002 --> 00:18:27,252
必须服役两年
for not less than two years...

272
00:18:27,342 --> 00:18:30,422
若是有需要...
and as much longer as may be required...

273
00:18:30,512 --> 00:18:32,672
我愿继续效忠部队
by the needs of the Federation.

274
00:18:33,802 --> 00:18:35,842
- 完了? - 谢谢
- All set? - Thank you.

275
00:18:40,062 --> 00:18:42,812
又来一批新兵
Fresh meat for the grinder, eh?

276
00:18:44,272 --> 00:18:48,112
- 你们的成绩如何? - 我要当飞行员
- So, how'd you kids do? - I'm gonna be a pilot.

277
00:18:48,192 --> 00:18:52,242
很好 我们很需要飞行员
Well, good for you. We need all the pilots we can get.

278
00:18:53,952 --> 00:18:56,822
- 你被分派到研发部门吗? - 没有
- Hey, did you get starside R and D? - No.

279
00:18:56,912 --> 00:19:00,412
- 不是吧? - 我要到战略理论部
- I don't believe it. - I got Games and Theory.

280
00:19:00,502 --> 00:19:02,542
战略理论?
Games and Theory?

281
00:19:02,622 --> 00:19:05,162
- 那是军事情报部 - 嗯
- That's military intelligence. - Yeah.

282
00:19:05,252 --> 00:19:07,542
好家伙 卡尔
Way to go, Carl.

283
00:19:07,632 --> 00:19:10,332
下次见面我就得向你敬礼
Next time we meet, I'll probably have to salute you.

284
00:19:10,422 --> 00:19:11,882
嗯
Hmm.

285
00:19:13,262 --> 00:19:15,172
你呢 孩子?
How about you, son?

286
00:19:15,262 --> 00:19:18,182
- 机动部队 长官 - 很好
- Infantry, sir. - Good for you.

287
00:19:18,272 --> 00:19:20,842
机动部队让我成为现在这样的男子汉
Mobile Infantry made me the man I am today.

288
00:19:22,522 --> 00:19:26,182
新兵必须在二十四小时内...
All recruits must report to the Federal Transportation Hub...

289
00:19:26,272 --> 00:19:27,902
到联邦运送站报到
within 2 4 hours.

290
00:19:27,982 --> 00:19:30,602
欢迎加入联邦军队的行列
Welcome to the adventure of Federal Service.

291
00:19:30,692 --> 00:19:32,982
咱们一起发誓
Let's make a vow.

292
00:19:33,072 --> 00:19:36,522
不管怎样 我们永远是朋友
No matter what, we'll always be friends.

293
00:19:38,242 --> 00:19:39,412
我同意
I'll go for that.

294
00:19:41,122 --> 00:19:43,452
我们恐怕不会再见面
Well, chances are we'll never see each other again.

295
00:19:45,212 --> 00:19:48,292
分隔几百万光年的距离
We'll be millions of light-years away from each other.

296
00:19:48,382 --> 00:19:50,872
不过 好呀 有何不可?
But, uh, yeah, sure. Why not?

297
00:19:53,432 --> 00:19:55,332
你给我去办退役
You'll resign, and that's all there is to it.

298
00:19:55,432 --> 00:19:58,302
虽然很没面子 不过也只能这样了
It may look bad, but if that's the worst you suffer, then that's fine.

299
00:19:58,392 --> 00:20:01,312
- 我不要退役 - 你一定要
- I won't quit! - I'm telling you, you will.

300
00:20:01,392 --> 00:20:03,472
你不能入伍 你要去渡假
You're not going back. You're going on vacation!

301
00:20:03,562 --> 00:20:05,472
我不去渡假
I am not going on vacation!

302
00:20:05,562 --> 00:20:07,352
我要当公民
I want to be a citizen.

303
00:20:07,442 --> 00:20:08,902
这是我的决定
It's my decision. I made it.

304
00:20:08,982 --> 00:20:10,892
你走出去找就不认你这儿子
You walk out that door, you are cut off, young man.

305
00:20:10,982 --> 00:20:12,562
懂吗?
You understand me?

306
00:20:12,652 --> 00:20:15,062
好吧 我不要你了
All right, that's it! You are cut off!

307
00:20:15,162 --> 00:20:17,062
你这是何必呢?
Johnny, why won't you change your mind?

308
00:20:17,162 --> 00:20:19,282
当公民这么重要吗?
Does citizenship mean that much to you?

309
00:20:20,162 --> 00:20:22,282
当然重要
Well, yeah, sure.

310
00:20:22,372 --> 00:20:24,282
希望如此
Well, I hope so.

311
00:20:24,372 --> 00:20:26,912
希望你别为了穿帅制服的...
I hope you don't ruin your life over some silly little girl...

312
00:20:27,002 --> 00:20:28,962
女孩而自毁前程
who wants to look handsome in a uniform.

313
00:20:29,042 --> 00:20:31,372
- 别这么说卡门 - 强尼
- Don't talk about Carmen that way! -Johnny.

314
00:20:37,842 --> 00:20:39,502
听到什么吗?
Do you have everything?

315
00:20:39,602 --> 00:20:41,472
好
Great.

316
00:20:47,022 --> 00:20:50,392
强尼
Johnny

317
00:20:50,482 --> 00:20:53,192
- 你迟到了 - 我父亲帮我收拾行李
- You're late. - My dad had to help me pack.

318
00:20:53,282 --> 00:20:56,032
他怕再也见不到我
Suddenly he's afraid he's never gonna see me again or something.

319
00:20:56,112 --> 00:20:58,602
他真好 不过很费时间
It was sweet, but it took forever.

320
00:20:58,702 --> 00:21:03,442
我猜我准备好了
Oh. Anyway, I guess I'm ready to go.

321
00:21:03,542 --> 00:21:06,542
我也是 我只剩这身衣服
Yeah, me too. I'm wearing everything I own.

322
00:21:09,382 --> 00:21:11,292
我很遗憾你的父母反对
I'm sorry your parents were mad.

323
00:21:11,382 --> 00:21:13,752
管它呢 反正...
Who cares? The Federation will give me...

324
00:21:13,842 --> 00:21:16,132
这两年军队会养我 对吧?
everything I need for the next two years, right?

325
00:21:17,762 --> 00:21:21,462
- 你和卡尔联络过吗? - 有 他早上就走了
- You talk to Carl? - Yeah, he left this morning.

326
00:21:21,562 --> 00:21:25,392
- 他不能说去哪里 - 能够入伍我好兴奋
- Couldn't say where. - Oh, it's exciting, going away.

327
00:21:25,482 --> 00:21:28,262
我也很害怕 你不会吗?
But I'm scared. Aren't you?

328
00:21:33,232 --> 00:21:35,142
我会很想你
I'm gonna miss you.

329
00:21:36,572 --> 00:21:38,812
我也会想你
I'm gonna miss you too.

330
00:21:39,742 --> 00:21:41,822
我爱你
I love you.

331
00:21:41,912 --> 00:21:44,992
前往特雷斯卡瓦的新兵准备启程
Outbound group 94B to Tereshkova...

332
00:21:45,082 --> 00:21:46,822
我该走了
That's me.

333
00:21:49,212 --> 00:21:53,162
说一次 试试看
Just say it once. Try it on for size.

334
00:21:56,842 --> 00:21:58,222
我爱你
I love you.

335
00:22:06,812 --> 00:22:08,932
别忘了写信给我
Don't forget to write.

336
00:22:09,022 --> 00:22:10,392
我不会忘的
I won't.

337
00:22:21,032 --> 00:22:23,672
"联邦电视网"

338
00:22:24,932 --> 00:22:28,282
"世界团结一致"
全自动步枪 谁想拿?
Fully automatic Morita. Who wants to hold it?

339
00:22:28,372 --> 00:22:29,622
我! 我! 我...
Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!

340
00:22:29,712 --> 00:22:34,002
公民万岁 人民创造美好明天
Citizen rule. People making a better tomorrow.

341
00:22:38,792 --> 00:22:42,122
"你想知道更多吗? "

342
00:22:42,302 --> 00:22:45,342
杀人犯今天被捕后接受审判
A murderer was captured this morning and tried today.

343
00:22:45,432 --> 00:22:47,342
有罪
Guilty.

344
00:22:48,682 --> 00:22:50,342
处以死刑
Sentence.: death.

345
00:22:50,442 --> 00:22:53,642
今晚六点行刑 实况转播
Execution tonight at 6.:00. All net. All channels.

346
00:22:54,162 --> 00:22:55,802
你想知道更多吗?

347
00:22:58,012 --> 00:22:59,382
"你能心灵感应吗? "

348
00:23:01,782 --> 00:23:04,702
如果你觉得能
If you think you're psychic,

349
00:23:04,782 --> 00:23:05,982
也许是真的
maybe you are.

350
00:23:08,292 --> 00:23:11,322
各地都在进行这项研究
Federal studies are being conducted in your community.

351
00:23:12,142 --> 00:23:14,162
你想知道更多吗? "警告"

352
00:23:14,712 --> 00:23:18,712
每个小学生都知道阿瑞克尼虫很危险
Every school kid knows that Arachnids are dangerous.

353
00:23:21,332 --> 00:23:27,302
"不宜观赏"
摩门教徒却罔顾联邦警告
However, Mormon extremists disregarded Federal warnings...

354
00:23:27,392 --> 00:23:31,642
在虫族隔离区建立教会
and established Fort Joe Smith deep inside the Arachnid Quarantine Zone.

355
00:23:31,732 --> 00:23:35,892
不料该地区早就被别人占领
Too late, they realized that Dantana had already been chosen by other colonists.:

356
00:23:35,982 --> 00:23:37,892
阿瑞克尼虫族
Arachnids.

357
00:23:38,402 --> 00:23:40,402
你想知道更多吗?

358
00:23:45,992 --> 00:23:48,992
- 一 二 三 四! - 你们大半都...
- One, two, three, four! - Most of you will not...

359
00:23:49,082 --> 00:23:51,782
熬不过魔鬼训练
live to be in the Mobile Infantry.

360
00:23:51,872 --> 00:23:54,542
因为你们都不够强
The trouble is, you are not good enough the way you are.

361
00:23:54,632 --> 00:23:56,752
手放好
Hands at your side!

362
00:23:56,842 --> 00:23:58,212
抬头挺胸
Chin up.

363
00:23:58,302 --> 00:24:01,082
我是你们的教官辛姆中士
I am your senior drill instructor, Career Sergeant Zim!

364
00:24:01,172 --> 00:24:04,012
小腹缩紧 双腿并拢
Suck in that gut! Feet together!

365
00:24:06,852 --> 00:24:09,172
我真是衰毙了
To think this had to happen to me.

366
00:24:09,262 --> 00:24:11,672
一群蠢蛋 算了
What a bunch of apes. No, strike that!

367
00:24:11,772 --> 00:24:13,052
你们逊毙了
You don't rate that good.

368
00:24:13,142 --> 00:24:15,182
我没见过...
Never in my life have I seen...

369
00:24:17,942 --> 00:24:20,152
你觉得很好笑?
Do you think I'm funny? Do I make you laugh?

370
00:24:20,232 --> 00:24:22,902
- 你觉得我是小丑吗? - 对不起
- Do you think I'm a comedian, son? - I'm sorry.

371
00:24:22,992 --> 00:24:27,112
你们随时都要尊称我为长官
The first words and the last words out of your stinking holes will be "Sir"!

372
00:24:27,202 --> 00:24:29,322
- 明白吗? - 明白 长官
- Do you get me? - Sir, yes, sir!

373
00:24:29,412 --> 00:24:31,872
绕着军营跑一圈
You see that armoury? Run around it.

374
00:24:31,952 --> 00:24:34,282
我叫你跑就跑
Run, I said! Run, run, run!

375
00:24:34,372 --> 00:24:36,372
- 布隆斯基 跟他跑! - 快! 快!
- Bronski, keep pace! - Move! Move!

376
00:24:36,462 --> 00:24:38,952
如果你们觉得我太狠太不公平
Now, anytime you think I'm being too tough...

377
00:24:39,042 --> 00:24:40,922
或是开始想念老妈
anytime you think I'm being unfair...

378
00:24:41,002 --> 00:24:44,502
那就马上退出
anytime you miss your mommy, quit!

379
00:24:44,592 --> 00:24:47,002
填好表格 签名 打包
You sign form 1240-A, you grab your gear...

380
00:24:47,092 --> 00:24:49,632
走上失败者的路
you take a stroll down Washout Lane!

381
00:24:49,722 --> 00:24:51,472
明不明白?
Do you get me?

382
00:24:51,562 --> 00:24:53,802
- 明白 长官! - 可悲
- Sir, yes, sir! - Pathetic!

383
00:24:53,892 --> 00:24:58,142
全是一群孬种 不知道这里有没有好汉
I wonder if there's a handful of guts in the whole bunch of you.

384
00:24:58,232 --> 00:25:03,272
谁认为他有办法打倒我?
Now, who here thinks they got what it takes to knock me down?

385
00:25:03,362 --> 00:25:06,152
我觉得我能 长官
Sir! I guess maybe I do, sir!

386
00:25:15,912 --> 00:25:19,282
哦! 天哪! 天哪!
Ow! God! God!

387
00:25:21,382 --> 00:25:23,582
- 你没事吧? - 没事 长官
- You all right, son? - Sir, yes, sir!

388
00:25:23,672 --> 00:25:26,962
我的手好像断了
It's my arm. I think it's broken, sir.

389
00:25:27,052 --> 00:25:29,922
- 医官! - 天哪
- Medic! - God.

390
00:25:30,012 --> 00:25:32,932
痛是心里想的
Pain is in your mind!

391
00:25:33,022 --> 00:25:34,922
- 下一个是谁? - 长官
- Who's next? - Sir!

392
00:25:35,022 --> 00:25:37,852
新兵弗洛斯报到 长官
Recruit Flores reporting for duty, sir!

393
00:25:47,282 --> 00:25:50,862
你特别要求转到这单位?
You specifically requested transfer from Fort Cronkite to this training unit?

394
00:25:50,952 --> 00:25:52,662
我听说这里是最严格的
Sir, I heard it was the best, sir!

395
00:25:52,742 --> 00:25:55,862
的确是最严格
It is the best.

396
00:25:55,952 --> 00:25:58,872
你凭什么以为自己够资格?
But what makes you think you're good enough?

397
00:26:05,802 --> 00:26:07,842
这女孩有种当班长
Now that's the kind of gal who makes squad leader.

398
00:26:07,932 --> 00:26:10,172
我才要当班长
That's my job you're talking about.

399
00:26:37,332 --> 00:26:39,122
我很想宰了辛姆中士
You know, I'd like to kill that Sergeant Zim.

400
00:26:39,212 --> 00:26:41,702
- 你的态度很不好 - 小心
- Whoa, improper attitude! - Watch it.

401
00:26:41,792 --> 00:26:43,922
- 这样会被踢出去 - 再见吧
- They'll kick you out for talking like that. - Bye-bye.

402
00:26:44,002 --> 00:26:46,082
你肯定会走上失败走路
There you go down Washout Lane.

403
00:26:46,172 --> 00:26:48,582
没种就是没种
Yup, you either got what it takes, or you don't.

404
00:26:48,672 --> 00:26:50,882
- 我们在排队 - 你也要等 王牌
- Hey, there is a line. - Wait your turn, Ace.

405
00:26:50,972 --> 00:26:54,632
别紧张 小兵 反正菜都很烂
Hey, at ease, little soldier. It's all the same muck.

406
00:26:54,722 --> 00:26:56,302
乖乖去排队
Get in line like everyone else.

407
00:27:06,442 --> 00:27:09,312
你这阔少爷真有种
You got some guts for a rich kid.

408
00:27:09,402 --> 00:27:11,892
咱们交个朋友 如何?
I guess you and me could be buddies. What do you say?

409
00:27:13,532 --> 00:27:16,702
- 真是荣幸 - 当然 我最够朋友了
- I'm honoured. - Hey! Of course you are.

410
00:27:16,792 --> 00:27:18,912
每个人都应该有个像我这样的朋友
Everybody should have a friend like me.

411
00:27:19,002 --> 00:27:21,242
王牌 到后面排队吧
Come on, Ace. Back of the line now! Back of the line!

412
00:27:22,712 --> 00:27:24,292
- 真是个混蛋 - 讨厌鬼
- What a jerk, man. - Tough guy.

413
00:27:26,422 --> 00:27:28,382
瑞哥 跟我一起吃饭
Hey, Rico, want to sit together?

414
00:27:28,462 --> 00:27:29,842
不 谢了
No thanks, Diz.

415
00:27:32,182 --> 00:27:34,092
你有什么问题?
What's your malfunction, Rico?

416
00:27:35,512 --> 00:27:37,472
你就是问题
You are.

417
00:27:37,562 --> 00:27:40,312
我想一个人入伍 你却硬要跟来
I joined up to get out on my own, and you had to tag along.

418
00:27:42,522 --> 00:27:44,812
你以为我为你入伍?
You think I joined the Mobile Infantry because of you?

419
00:27:44,902 --> 00:27:46,812
你敢说不是?
You saying you didn't?

420
00:27:53,242 --> 00:27:54,482
嗨
Hi.

421
00:27:54,572 --> 00:27:57,152
想都别想 王牌 你不行的
Forget about it, Ace. You don't stand a chance.

422
00:27:57,242 --> 00:28:00,112
难道你就能当班长?
What makes you even think you're gonna make squad leader, Rico?

423
00:28:00,202 --> 00:28:01,862
- 我比你有料 - 哈!
- Something I got, you don't. - Ha!

424
00:28:01,962 --> 00:28:04,742
- 有钱少爷只会装阔 - 才不
- You rich kids are all the same. - It isn't about that.

425
00:28:04,832 --> 00:28:06,962
- 这得靠能力 - 嘿!
- It's about who's the best. - Hey!

426
00:28:18,312 --> 00:28:19,802
第三班
Third squad!

427
00:28:26,612 --> 00:28:29,562
长官 我不懂
Sir, I don't understand.

428
00:28:29,652 --> 00:28:31,892
在核战争中何必用刀?
Who needs a knife in a nuke fight, anyway?

429
00:28:31,992 --> 00:28:35,652
只要按下按钮就行 长官
All you gotta do is push a button, sir.

430
00:28:35,742 --> 00:28:40,152
暂停 手放在墙上 伞兵
Cease fire. Put your hand on that wall, trooper.

431
00:28:43,582 --> 00:28:45,742
把手放在墙上
Put your hand on that wall!

432
00:28:55,512 --> 00:28:56,882
该死
Damn it.

433
00:29:01,852 --> 00:29:06,062
敌人的手掌受伤就不能按钮
The enemy cannot push a button if you disable his hand.

434
00:29:09,862 --> 00:29:11,062
医官
Medic!

435
00:29:13,902 --> 00:29:16,392
我们有一个共同点
Ah, well, we all have one thing in common.

436
00:29:16,492 --> 00:29:19,412
我们都蠢到要参加机动部队
We were all stupid enough to sign up for Mobile Infantry.

437
00:29:19,492 --> 00:29:22,582
- 布雷肯瑞奇 你为何加入? - 我全家都是农夫
- Breckinridge, what's your excuse? - Oh, my family's all farmers.

438
00:29:22,662 --> 00:29:24,572
我讨厌务农 而机动部队...
I hate farming. I mean, uh, Mobile Infantry...

439
00:29:24,662 --> 00:29:26,572
比起来就像是在野餐
It's like pure picnic by comparison.

440
00:29:26,672 --> 00:29:30,082
乡巴佬真是又蠢又壮对不对?
All right, so they grow 'em big and dumb on the farm planet, huh?

441
00:29:30,172 --> 00:29:32,542
- 而且帅! - 我就爱壮汉
- And pretty! - I like big!

442
00:29:32,632 --> 00:29:35,582
- 蒂嘉娜 你呢? - 我想要从政
- Djana'D, what about you? - Oh, I'm going in for politics...

443
00:29:35,672 --> 00:29:37,752
想从政就得成为公民
and, you know, you gotta be a citizen for that.

444
00:29:37,842 --> 00:29:40,932
- 所以我就来了 - 你想负起责任
- So here I am. - Ah, you want some responsibility.

445
00:29:41,012 --> 00:29:44,262
- 对 - 苏杰米 接着说吧
- Yeah. - Shujimi, come on, let's keep it goin'.

446
00:29:44,352 --> 00:29:46,762
我被哈佛大学取录
I got into Harvard, but my father says forget it.

447
00:29:46,852 --> 00:29:48,102
可是我老爸嫌学费太贵
It's gonna cost an arm and a leg, you know?

448
00:29:48,192 --> 00:29:49,892
只要服役
So, if I serve,

449
00:29:49,982 --> 00:29:52,602
就能赚取学费
Federation pays my way.

450
00:29:52,692 --> 00:29:54,102
我想生孩子
I want to have babies.

451
00:29:54,192 --> 00:29:56,482
公民比较容易申请执照
You know, it's a lot easier to get a licence if you've served.

452
00:29:56,572 --> 00:29:58,282
- 然后呢... - 我要当职业军官
- So... - I'm going career.

453
00:29:58,362 --> 00:30:01,072
按步就班升上去
Officer's training. All the way.

454
00:30:01,162 --> 00:30:03,452
未来的星际元帅 瑞哥 该你了
Future Sky Marshal. All right, Rico, your turn.

455
00:30:06,042 --> 00:30:07,452
不要多管闲事
Who asked you to be so nosy?

456
00:30:07,542 --> 00:30:09,622
怎么? 我是坏人吗? 我想当作家
What? I'm the-the bad guy? I'm gonna be a writer, you know?

457
00:30:09,712 --> 00:30:12,462
当然能管闲事
A writer's got a right to be nosy.

458
00:30:12,542 --> 00:30:15,332
弗洛雷斯 你和瑞哥都来自布宜诺斯艾利斯
Hey, Flores, you know Rico from Buenos Aires.

459
00:30:15,422 --> 00:30:19,632
- 他为什么入伍? - 哦
- What's his story? - Oh, uh,

460
00:30:19,722 --> 00:30:21,712
他是为了一个女孩子
he's here because of a girl.

461
00:30:22,552 --> 00:30:26,092
瑞哥 大情圣
Oh, Rico! Lover boy!

462
00:30:27,562 --> 00:30:30,482
- 他让我感到兴奋 - 他一定会打你
- He's getting me excited. - He's gonna blow.

463
00:30:34,022 --> 00:30:35,192
为了你吗?
Is it you?

464
00:30:39,242 --> 00:30:43,982
这是我们的宿舍 很简陋 不过是我的家
This is where we live. It's not much, but it's home.

465
00:30:44,082 --> 00:30:47,742
这是我的床铺 我每晚都梦到你
Right there, that's my bunk, where I dream about you every night.

466
00:30:49,252 --> 00:30:50,832
训练很辛苦
Boot's pretty tough.

467
00:30:50,922 --> 00:30:53,542
有时我很灰心
Sometimes I think I won't make it.

468
00:30:53,632 --> 00:30:55,922
不过我一想到你就会更努力
But then I think about what you're doing, and I try harder.

469
00:30:57,842 --> 00:31:02,172
- 嘿 你介意吗? - 努力点 宝贝
- Hey, guys! Do you mind? - Try harder, baby, try harder!

470
00:31:06,642 --> 00:31:10,692
谁知道? 也许我会成为班长
Who knows? They might even make me squad leader.

471
00:31:10,772 --> 00:31:12,512
我得上床了
Uh-oh, I better pack it in.

472
00:31:12,602 --> 00:31:16,192
我爱你 宝贝 我爱你!
Oh, I love you, baby, I love you!

473
00:31:16,282 --> 00:31:19,942
- 写信给我 - 我是如此爱你
- Write me! - I love you so much

474
00:31:20,032 --> 00:31:22,732
- 我要杀了你 - 我是如此爱你
- I'm gonna kill you guys! - I love you so much

475
00:31:25,582 --> 00:31:26,822
- 再见 记得写信 - 再见!
- Bye! Write me. - Bye!

476
00:31:28,702 --> 00:31:30,782
五分钟后绕行月球 艾邦妮兹
Orbit in five, Ibanez.

477
00:31:30,872 --> 00:31:32,702
先到先飞
First one there gets to fly.

478
00:31:48,392 --> 00:31:50,552
- 关闭舱门 - 等一下
- Locking it down. - Wait! Wait!

479
00:31:52,602 --> 00:31:55,392
别让艾邦妮兹驾驶 她太疯狂了
Oh, no. Not Ibanez again. She's crazy!

480
00:31:55,482 --> 00:31:57,522
准备 发射
Ready, go!

481
00:32:04,112 --> 00:32:05,442
好!
Yeah!

482
00:32:07,282 --> 00:32:08,782
伸出机翼
Deploying wings.

483
00:32:52,872 --> 00:32:55,282
你干嘛这么开心?
How come you're in such a good mood, huh?

484
00:32:55,372 --> 00:32:57,202
今天我要开战舰
'Cause today I get to fly that.

485
00:33:20,652 --> 00:33:23,062
飞行受训人员艾邦妮兹报到
Pilot Trainee Ibanez reporting for duty, ma'am.

486
00:33:23,152 --> 00:33:24,982
坐在副驾驶座
Take the number two chair, Ibanez.

487
00:33:25,072 --> 00:33:27,312
- 是的 女士 - 看见啦?
- Yes, ma'am. - You see that?

488
00:33:30,662 --> 00:33:35,872
- 辨识身份 - 艾邦妮兹 T325A 正确
- Identify. - Ibanez, T-3 25-A, clear.

489
00:33:40,922 --> 00:33:44,002
你在这儿干嘛?
What are you doing here?

490
00:33:44,092 --> 00:33:46,962
我要教你驾驶这艘战舰
I'm the guy whose gonna teach you to fly this crate.

491
00:33:47,052 --> 00:33:49,842
助理教官
Oh, Assistant Instructor.

492
00:33:50,932 --> 00:33:53,422
我该尊称你长官吗?
Should I call you "sir"?

493
00:33:53,522 --> 00:33:56,472
- 我下命令才要 - 准备起飞
- Only when I give you an order. - Prepare for departure.

494
00:33:57,982 --> 00:34:01,562
没想到我们会再见面
It's amazing, us running into each other like this.

495
00:34:01,652 --> 00:34:04,402
- 也许是命中注定 - 也许不是
- Maybe it's fate. - Maybe not.

496
00:34:04,482 --> 00:34:07,652
我听说有个女孩很优秀
Heard about this crazy girl coming through the Academy.

497
00:34:07,742 --> 00:34:12,362
她是天生好手 只是有点野
Solid math, a little wild on the stick, but a natural.

498
00:34:12,452 --> 00:34:13,912
我知道是你
And when it turned out to be you,

499
00:34:13,992 --> 00:34:16,202
就安排和你见面
I just made sure that we would run into each other.

500
00:34:16,292 --> 00:34:18,992
杨罗杰号可以起飞
Rodger Young cleared for undocking and departure.

501
00:34:19,082 --> 00:34:20,912
好了 艾邦妮兹
All right, Ibanez.

502
00:34:21,002 --> 00:34:23,332
- 开出去吧 - 是的 女士
- Take her out. - Yes, ma'am.

503
00:34:24,632 --> 00:34:26,542
系统正常
All systems go.

504
00:34:50,492 --> 00:34:54,072
进行模拟飞行时老师都跟不上我
In simulation, my supervisors could never keep up.

505
00:34:54,162 --> 00:34:55,952
这不是模拟飞行
Well, this isn't simulation any more...

506
00:34:56,042 --> 00:34:58,662
小心点 军校生
so take her out easy, cadet.

507
00:34:58,752 --> 00:35:00,032
是的 长官
Yes, sir.

508
00:35:09,092 --> 00:35:10,632
距离五米
Five metres from object.

509
00:35:13,802 --> 00:35:15,352
距离三米
Three metres from object.

510
00:35:20,102 --> 00:35:21,432
通过
Clear.

511
00:35:24,442 --> 00:35:27,392
- 别超过起飞速限 - 否则呢?
- Don't exceed port speed. - Or what?

512
00:35:27,482 --> 00:35:32,192
你的飞行权会被取消 还有我的
Or they revoke your flight status, and mine.

513
00:35:33,952 --> 00:35:36,322
你的前途掌握在我手上
Your career is in my hands.

514
00:35:43,502 --> 00:35:44,882
慢慢来 副驾驶
Steady as she goes, Number Two.

515
00:35:44,962 --> 00:35:47,202
- 准备超光速飞行 - 是的
- Prepare for warp. - Yes, ma'am.

516
00:35:47,302 --> 00:35:50,552
一号 计算木星航道
Number One, design for Jupiter orbit.

517
00:35:50,632 --> 00:35:54,462
准备转换超光速引擎
All crew, all sections, stand by to cut in C-drive.

518
00:35:54,552 --> 00:35:58,302
五...四...
Star drive in five, four...

519
00:35:58,392 --> 00:36:00,682
准备 稳定...
ready, steady...

520
00:36:00,772 --> 00:36:02,312
启动
go!

521
00:36:26,342 --> 00:36:28,162
快进攻 快!
We're going in! Move!

522
00:36:37,222 --> 00:36:38,632
我们冲不破防线
Man, they're defended. No way in.

523
00:36:41,102 --> 00:36:43,472
- 翻跳动作 - 什么?
- Flip six, three hole. - What?

524
00:36:43,562 --> 00:36:46,312
你做翻跳动作就能得分
You run a flip six, three hole play, and you can score.

525
00:36:46,402 --> 00:36:47,772
- 掩护我 - 好
- Cover me. - You got it.

526
00:36:56,242 --> 00:36:57,862
上吧
Now!

527
00:37:04,462 --> 00:37:06,952
- 谢了 哥们 - 杂种
- Thanks, buddy. - Bastard!

528
00:37:16,092 --> 00:37:17,472
嗯!
Yeah!

529
00:37:23,102 --> 00:37:25,142
那小子很灵活
Kid's got some moves.

530
00:37:25,232 --> 00:37:27,102
让他当班长 看看他的能耐
Give him a squad. See what he can do.

531
00:37:32,112 --> 00:37:33,902
凯蒂 凯蒂
Kitty, Kitty.

532
00:37:33,992 --> 00:37:36,482
我得教你们打台球
Someone's got to teach you guys how to play some pool here.

533
00:37:37,742 --> 00:37:39,152
瞧他
Look at him.

534
00:37:39,242 --> 00:37:41,992
那副得意样 真自傲
Have you ever seen anybody so pleased with himself?

535
00:37:42,082 --> 00:37:45,742
辛姆一定得选个乖乖牌
Well, Zim must have had to choose someone to be his brownnose.

536
00:37:51,882 --> 00:37:53,712
没有你我就办不到
I couldn't have done it without you, Diz.

537
00:37:55,592 --> 00:37:56,922
朋友?
Friends?

538
00:37:59,722 --> 00:38:01,182
朋友
Friends.

539
00:38:02,432 --> 00:38:05,002
- 信来了 李维 - 我就是
- Mail call! Levy! - Yeah, that's me.

540
00:38:05,102 --> 00:38:07,672
- 苏杰米 - 在
- Shujimi! - Here.

541
00:38:07,772 --> 00:38:09,182
- 瑞哥 - 在
- Rico. - Here.

542
00:38:09,272 --> 00:38:11,312
- 布雷肯瑞奇 - 嗯 在
- Breckinridge! - Yeah, right here.

543
00:38:11,402 --> 00:38:14,522
- 泰勒 - 我在这儿
- Niler. - Yeah, here I am. Ah, great, my dad.

544
00:38:14,612 --> 00:38:16,572
没了 大伙
That's all, folks.

545
00:38:24,082 --> 00:38:25,542
嗨 强尼
Hi, Johnny.

546
00:38:25,622 --> 00:38:28,192
抱歉没早点写信给你
I'm sorry I haven't written you sooner, but, uh...

547
00:38:28,292 --> 00:38:30,862
噢...瑞哥 你配不上她
Oh, Rico,it's been really busy.you don't deserve that!

548
00:38:30,962 --> 00:38:32,922
- 嘘 嘘 - 他们真的在这里
- Shh, shh. - They've really got us going here.

549
00:38:33,002 --> 00:38:35,542
你一定当上班长
They must have made you squad leader by now.

550
00:38:35,632 --> 00:38:38,042
没有的话 叫他们来找我
And if they haven't, tell 'em to talk to me.

551
00:38:38,132 --> 00:38:40,382
你瞧 找到好女人就不用愁
See? All it takes is the love of a good woman.

552
00:38:42,972 --> 00:38:45,722
- 看这儿 - 别看了
- Look at that.Look at those. - Stop it.

553
00:38:45,812 --> 00:38:47,722
不是很美吗?
Isn't it beautiful?

554
00:38:47,812 --> 00:38:49,932
我好爱这儿
I love it out here.

555
00:38:52,152 --> 00:38:54,772
这就是问题
That's also the problem

556
00:38:54,862 --> 00:38:59,072
因为 我想当职业军人
Because I think I'm gonna go career.

557
00:39:00,412 --> 00:39:02,782
我要指挥战舰
I want to command a ship of my own.

558
00:39:02,872 --> 00:39:04,742
这样一来...
And you know...

559
00:39:06,502 --> 00:39:07,912
我们就没时间
I don't think that's gonna leave a lot of room...

560
00:39:08,002 --> 00:39:10,072
交往 强尼
for you and me, Johnny.

561
00:39:13,542 --> 00:39:17,082
我知道你会很失望
I know that's not what you wanted to hear.

562
00:39:17,172 --> 00:39:18,422
可是
But, uh...

563
00:39:20,682 --> 00:39:25,012
我得把握机会 对不起
I have to follow my heart. I'm sorry.

564
00:39:27,062 --> 00:39:30,092
写信给我
Write me, all right?

565
00:39:30,192 --> 00:39:32,762
让我们永远当好朋友
Write me so that I know we'll always be friends.

566
00:39:47,952 --> 00:39:51,122
- 让我们回到游戏 - 我觉得很对不起强尼
- Let's get back to the game. - I feel so sorry for Johnny.

567
00:39:51,212 --> 00:39:52,542
她们总是伤透你的心
Funny how they always want to be friends...

568
00:39:52,622 --> 00:39:55,462
之后还想做好朋友
after they rip your guts out, huh?

569
00:39:55,542 --> 00:39:58,332
我是活该
Yeah. Well, it's what I deserve.

570
00:39:59,842 --> 00:40:01,752
什么意思?
What are you talking about?

571
00:40:03,592 --> 00:40:05,472
我会入伍全是为了她
Oh, I joined up for her.

572
00:40:06,852 --> 00:40:09,092
没有她我就不会来
I wouldn't even be here if it wasn't for her.

573
00:40:09,182 --> 00:40:11,972
你在说什么? 你是靠自己当上班长
What are you talking about? You made squad leader on your own.

574
00:40:14,772 --> 00:40:17,352
至少你还有我差遣
And, hey, you still got me to kick around.

575
00:40:22,072 --> 00:40:23,482
好日子结束了
Fun and games are over, children.

576
00:40:23,572 --> 00:40:25,612
今天要进行
You will be firing live ammunition...

577
00:40:25,702 --> 00:40:27,942
实弹的模拟战斗
in a simulated combat environment.

578
00:40:28,042 --> 00:40:32,412
你们千万要小心进行
You will exercise extreme caution on my assault course!

579
00:40:32,502 --> 00:40:35,252
- 你们都明白了吗? - 明白 长官
- Do you get me? - Sir, yes, sir!

580
00:40:35,332 --> 00:40:37,162
瑞哥 带队出去
Rico, take 'em out!

581
00:40:38,632 --> 00:40:41,802
第一组跟我来 第二组十秒钟后出发
First fire team with me. Next team in ten seconds.

582
00:40:41,882 --> 00:40:44,722
最高分是180
Maximum score has been 2 80.

583
00:40:44,802 --> 00:40:48,722
- 你们一定要更好 - 上吧
- I expect you to do better! - Go!

584
00:40:56,942 --> 00:40:58,682
苏杰米 趴下来
Shujimi, stay down!

585
00:41:07,742 --> 00:41:11,112
该死 布雷肯瑞奇 别挡住我
Hey! Goddam it, Breckinridge, clear my line of fire!

586
00:41:11,202 --> 00:41:13,162
我的头盔坏了
It's my helmet! It's all screwed up!

587
00:41:13,252 --> 00:41:14,992
你会碍事的
You're gonna blow the score!

588
00:41:15,082 --> 00:41:16,622
- 蠢蛋 - 妈的!
- Damn! - Dumb shit!

589
00:41:16,712 --> 00:41:18,122
快前进 怎么了?
Diz, stay put! What's the problem?

590
00:41:18,212 --> 00:41:20,002
- 头盔有问题 - 给我
- Damn thing keeps getting in my way! - Give it to me.

591
00:41:20,092 --> 00:41:22,382
每次出错都是你的问题
How come whenever something goes wrong, it's always you, Breckinridge?

592
00:41:22,462 --> 00:41:23,882
那是因为我又蠢又壮
It must be 'cause I'm big and dumb!

593
00:41:23,972 --> 00:41:25,592
没错
Yeah, right!

594
00:41:31,642 --> 00:41:33,512
医官
Medic!

595
00:41:36,312 --> 00:41:39,932
瑞哥 你被解除班长职位
Rico, you are relieved of squad command!

596
00:41:41,982 --> 00:41:44,992
是你准许新兵脱下头盔吗?
Rico, did you give the recruit permission to remove his helmet?

597
00:41:45,072 --> 00:41:47,942
是的 长官 布雷肯瑞奇说他的头盔坏了
Sir, yes, sir. Breckinridge reported a helmet malfunction...

598
00:41:48,032 --> 00:41:49,662
我要他拿给我看
and I asked him to show it to me, sir.

599
00:41:49,742 --> 00:41:53,492
你会修理M-3型头盔吗?
Are you rated to repair the M-3 Tactical Helmet, Rico?

600
00:41:55,212 --> 00:41:56,662
不会 长官
Sir, no, sir!

601
00:41:56,752 --> 00:41:58,662
那么你为何在实弹演习时...
Then why did you order your man to remove his helmet...

602
00:41:58,752 --> 00:42:01,322
叫他脱下头盔?
during a live fire exercise?

603
00:42:01,422 --> 00:42:04,622
我需要每名队员尽全力
Sir, I needed everyone in my squad operational, sir!

604
00:42:06,092 --> 00:42:08,552
我想要获胜 长官
I wanted to win, sir!

605
00:42:14,472 --> 00:42:15,852
继续
Carry on.

606
00:42:23,282 --> 00:42:27,902
军士 我们因为此事失去两名新兵
Sergeant, we've already lost two recruits over this incident.

607
00:42:27,992 --> 00:42:31,072
你认为这个人还有前途吗?
Do you think there's any possibility of salvaging this man?

608
00:42:32,912 --> 00:42:34,242
有的 长官
Yes, sir, I do.

609
00:42:35,582 --> 00:42:36,912
好吧
All right.

610
00:42:38,462 --> 00:42:40,282
让他接受行政处罚
We'll try administrative punishment.

611
00:42:46,132 --> 00:42:48,012
囚犯 站住
Prisoner, halt!

612
00:43:05,862 --> 00:43:07,772
用力咬
Bite down on this, son.

613
00:43:07,862 --> 00:43:10,402
很有用 我很清楚
It helps. I know.

614
00:43:20,752 --> 00:43:23,792
因为他指挥无能
For incompetence of command...

615
00:43:23,882 --> 00:43:26,502
在实弹演习中...
for failure to abide by safety regulations...

616
00:43:26,592 --> 00:43:30,002
违反安全规定...
during a live fire exercise...

617
00:43:30,092 --> 00:43:33,762
因为他的疏失导致一名士兵死亡
for negligence which contributed to the death of a teammate...

618
00:43:33,852 --> 00:43:36,092
新兵强尼·瑞哥
recruit trainee John Rico...

619
00:43:36,182 --> 00:43:38,262
必须受刑...
is sentenced to administrative punishment.

620
00:43:39,942 --> 00:43:41,102
十下鞭刑
Ten lashes.

621
00:43:43,112 --> 00:43:45,012
开始行刑
You may carry out the sentence.

622
00:43:52,322 --> 00:43:54,362
一...
One!

623
00:43:55,912 --> 00:43:57,952
二...
Two!

624
00:43:59,752 --> 00:44:01,122
三...
Three!

625
00:44:03,132 --> 00:44:05,032
四...
Four!

626
00:44:07,052 --> 00:44:08,672
五...
Five!

627
00:44:11,222 --> 00:44:12,332
六...
Six!

628
00:44:14,222 --> 00:44:15,422
七...
Seven!

629
00:44:17,222 --> 00:44:19,802
八...
Eight!

630
00:44:19,892 --> 00:44:21,222
九...
Nine!

631
00:44:22,902 --> 00:44:24,272
十!
Ten!

632
00:44:46,592 --> 00:44:48,462
谢了 你猜中我的心意
Thanks. You read my mind.

633
00:44:50,302 --> 00:44:53,422
下半夜更最难熬
Oh, third watch always seems to last forever.

634
00:44:53,512 --> 00:44:55,172
不一定
I don't know.

635
00:44:55,262 --> 00:44:57,722
这得看你和谁一起值班
It depends on who you're spending it with.

636
00:45:00,522 --> 00:45:02,342
出了问题
Something's wrong.

637
00:45:06,812 --> 00:45:10,812
- 那儿 - 我重新设定航道
- There. - No, I replotted the course.

638
00:45:10,902 --> 00:45:14,072
- 这样更有效率 - 你才来了三个星期...
- It's more efficient this way. - Three weeks aboard a starship...

639
00:45:14,152 --> 00:45:16,402
就想跟我比?
and you think that you can lick my navs?

640
00:45:16,492 --> 00:45:17,742
尽管查
Check it.

641
00:45:22,912 --> 00:45:26,002
我和达拉第舰长谈过
You know, I was talking with Captain Deladier...

642
00:45:26,082 --> 00:45:27,542
她说...
and, uh, she said...

643
00:45:27,632 --> 00:45:30,202
别转移话题
Don't change the subject.

644
00:45:30,302 --> 00:45:31,542
我对不对?
Am I right?

645
00:45:38,972 --> 00:45:41,972
"新航道最佳" 你做得对
Yeah. Yeah. You're right.

646
00:45:42,062 --> 00:45:44,382
那么舰长怎么说?
So, what did the captain say?

647
00:45:45,812 --> 00:45:48,562
她说我们应该正式搭档...
She thinks that we ought to team up officially...

648
00:45:50,612 --> 00:45:53,392
为她服务
and crew for her.

649
00:45:53,492 --> 00:45:56,982
- 你和我? - 我们是好搭档 卡门
- You and me, huh? - We're good together, Carmen.

650
00:45:57,072 --> 00:46:00,412
各方面都领先
We're way ahead of the curve in every department.

651
00:46:00,492 --> 00:46:03,492
我们很有默契
I can anticipate you.

652
00:46:03,582 --> 00:46:06,332
你知道我要什么
You know what I want.

653
00:46:08,002 --> 00:46:11,252
我不知道 你要什么?
No. What do you want?

654
00:46:19,092 --> 00:46:20,922
太空中有重力场
There's a gravity field out there.

655
00:46:23,222 --> 00:46:25,512
- 进行扫瞄 启动 - 那儿
- Run a scan. Sensors on. - There.

656
00:46:28,192 --> 00:46:31,442
- 重力2.25 继续增加... - 报告
- Gravity at 225 and rising. - Report.

657
00:46:31,522 --> 00:46:33,482
船长 前方有不明物体
Captain, we're in the path of an unidentified object...

658
00:46:33,572 --> 00:46:35,282
向我们快速冲来...
moving toward us at high speed.

659
00:46:35,362 --> 00:46:37,652
根据资料应该是小行星
Profile suggests an asteroid, ma'am.

660
00:46:49,682 --> 00:46:52,622
"撞击警告"
- 六秒后撞击 - 紧急闪躲动作
- Impact, six seconds! - Emergency evasion!

661
00:46:57,632 --> 00:47:00,122
三...二...
Three, two,

662
00:47:03,222 --> 00:47:04,502
启动
fire!

663
00:47:19,402 --> 00:47:21,152
关闭21号舱门
Close compartment 21!

664
00:47:35,302 --> 00:47:36,712
从哪儿来的?
Where'd it come from?

665
00:47:36,802 --> 00:47:39,632
从虫族隔离区来的
It came out of the Arachnid Quarantine Zone, ma'am.

666
00:47:41,592 --> 00:47:44,512
通讯官通知舰队小行星接近中
Number Four, contact Fleet. Tell 'em there's a loose asteroid headed their way.

667
00:47:44,602 --> 00:47:46,722
通讯失效 全都被摧毁
Communications are down, ma'am. They're gone.

668
00:47:48,432 --> 00:47:51,352
- 估计损失 - 舰身受损
- Damage assessment. - Hull's compromised.

669
00:47:51,442 --> 00:47:52,932
我们没死掉真走运
We're lucky to be alive, ma'am.

670
00:47:53,022 --> 00:47:54,902
这不是靠运气
Luck didn't have anything to do with it.

671
00:47:56,232 --> 00:47:58,062
我们的飞行小组很优秀
We have a hell of a flight team.

672
00:48:13,462 --> 00:48:15,832
你不能离开
It really stinks, you going.

673
00:48:15,922 --> 00:48:18,752
机动部队没有我也一样
Yeah, well, the Mobile Infantry will just have to get along without me.

674
00:48:22,972 --> 00:48:25,802
我不懂 瑞哥 你接受了惩罚
I don't get it, Rico. You took your licks.

675
00:48:25,892 --> 00:48:27,552
如果他们不想要你 可以把你踢走
If they didn't want you, they would have kicked you out.

676
00:48:27,642 --> 00:48:29,022
嘿...
Hey...

677
00:48:30,522 --> 00:48:32,562
我不该入伍 我害死人...
I joined up for the wrong reasons. I got a guy killed.

678
00:48:32,642 --> 00:48:34,972
这就证明我没有能力
I figure that kind of proves I don't have what it takes.

679
00:48:35,062 --> 00:48:38,602
瑞哥 电话接通了
Rico, your call's going through.

680
00:48:38,692 --> 00:48:40,572
去接
Take it there.

681
00:48:46,662 --> 00:48:50,952
- 喂? 强尼 - 嗨 妈妈
- Hello? Oh, Johnny! - Hi, Mom.

682
00:48:51,042 --> 00:48:53,082
比尔 快接电话 是强尼
B-Bill, pick it up. It's Johnny!

683
00:48:53,172 --> 00:48:54,962
- 强尼? - 爸爸
- Johnny? - Dad.

684
00:48:55,042 --> 00:48:56,422
- 你的制服呢? - 比尔...
- Where's your uniform? - Bill.

685
00:48:58,252 --> 00:49:00,162
见到你真好
It's just good to hear from you.

686
00:49:00,262 --> 00:49:02,542
你好吗? 儿子?
How are you, son?

687
00:49:02,632 --> 00:49:04,872
我不适合这里 爸爸
It's not really working out here for me, Dad.

688
00:49:04,972 --> 00:49:06,462
我在想...
I was thinking...

689
00:49:06,552 --> 00:49:08,462
不知道我能不能回家
I was hoping it would be all right if I came home.

690
00:49:08,562 --> 00:49:11,592
当然能 马上回来
Well, of-of course. You should come home immediately.

691
00:49:13,022 --> 00:49:15,262
对不起 我太傻了
I'm sorry. I've been an idiot.

692
00:49:15,352 --> 00:49:17,642
别这么说 你先回家...
Don't talk like that. You just come on home...

693
00:49:17,732 --> 00:49:18,932
咱们再好好谈谈
talk things out.

694
00:49:20,532 --> 00:49:21,852
我们很爱你 儿子
We love you, son.

695
00:49:23,362 --> 00:49:25,942
- 那是什么? - 好像要下雨
- My, what's that? - Looks like rain.

696
00:49:26,032 --> 00:49:28,702
- 这时候? - 外面好暗
- This time of year? - Sure is dark.

697
00:49:28,782 --> 00:49:30,492
大气干扰导致...
Your transmission has been terminated...

698
00:49:30,582 --> 00:49:33,122
通讯中断
due to atmospheric interference.

699
00:49:33,212 --> 00:49:34,662
请稍后再试
Please try your call again later.

700
00:49:41,382 --> 00:49:42,962
再见了
Well, see ya.

701
00:49:43,052 --> 00:49:46,462
你就这样退出...
Hey, you take that stroll down Washout Lane...

702
00:49:46,552 --> 00:49:48,382
只证明一件事
you're only proving one thing,Johnny.

703
00:49:48,472 --> 00:49:49,802
什么事?
What's that, Diz?

704
00:49:53,392 --> 00:49:56,232
你没有资格当公民
That you don't have what it takes to be a citizen.

705
00:50:25,092 --> 00:50:26,582
什么事?
What's happening?

706
00:50:32,262 --> 00:50:33,682
嗨 发生什么事?
Hey, hey, what's going on?

707
00:50:33,772 --> 00:50:35,512
发生什么事?
Wh-What's going on?

708
00:50:35,602 --> 00:50:39,182
- 嗨 Kitten 怎么回事? - 战争 我们要去参战了...
- Hey, Kitten, what's going on? - It's war! We're going to war!

709
00:50:43,612 --> 00:50:47,232
这次的灾难前所未有
The devastation we are seeing is unparalleled.

710
00:50:47,322 --> 00:50:52,202
根据估计有数百万人丧命 一座城市全毁
