884
01:05:10,432 --> 01:05:12,512
大K星的战场
are calling Big K...

885
01:05:12,602 --> 01:05:15,092
第六机动部队展开攻击
with the 6th Mobile Infantry Division.

886
01:05:15,192 --> 01:05:18,192
这丑陋的星球全是大虫
It's an ugly planet, a bug planet.

887
01:05:18,272 --> 01:05:20,352
威胁人类的生存...
A planet hostile to life as we...

888
01:05:25,872 --> 01:05:27,362
救命啊!
Help me!

889
01:05:31,542 --> 01:05:32,872
快向右
Squad right!

890
01:05:44,882 --> 01:05:47,642
快走 快 快 快...
Come on! Go, go, go!

891
01:05:47,722 --> 01:05:49,382
快离开这里
Get out of here now!

892
01:05:50,972 --> 01:05:53,132
- 小心点! - 小心你的侧面! 小心你的侧面!
- Watch your step! - Watch your flank! Watch your flank!

893
01:05:53,232 --> 01:05:55,052
我们被击溃
GXR, we're being overrun.

894
01:06:04,992 --> 01:06:07,232
基顿 不!
Kitten, no!

895
01:06:38,352 --> 01:06:39,772
哦 天哪
Oh, God!

896
01:06:39,862 --> 01:06:43,942
哦 天哪 哦
Oh, God! Oh! Oh!

897
01:07:00,682 --> 01:07:04,612
"联邦电视网"

898
01:07:06,112 --> 01:07:08,752
"一小时内十万人丧命"

899
01:07:13,222 --> 01:07:14,882
人类面临空前危机
Crisis for humankind.

900
01:07:14,972 --> 01:07:17,302
舰队官员承认他们...
Fleet officials admit they underestimated...

901
01:07:17,392 --> 01:07:20,812
低估虫族的防卫能力
the Arachnids' defensive capability.

902
01:07:20,902 --> 01:07:23,472
因为克兰达夫星的惨剧
Accepting responsibility for Klendathu...

903
01:07:23,572 --> 01:07:26,142
狄恩元帅引咎辞职
Sky Marshal Dienes resigns.

904
01:07:26,242 --> 01:07:28,812
新任的元帅马休...
His successor, Sky Marshal Tahat Meru...

905
01:07:28,902 --> 01:07:31,482
宣布她的战略
outlines her new strategy.

906
01:07:31,572 --> 01:07:33,482
我们必须
To fight the bug...

907
01:07:33,582 --> 01:07:35,982
了解虫族才能致胜
we must understand the bug.

908
01:07:36,082 --> 01:07:39,202
我们绝对不能再重蹈克兰达夫的覆辙
We can ill afford another Klendathu.

909
01:07:39,952 --> 01:07:41,602
你想知道更多吗?

910
01:07:41,712 --> 01:07:43,792
联邦科学家想...
Federal scientists struggle to explain...

911
01:07:43,882 --> 01:07:46,712
解释虫族的军事智慧
the intelligent military actions of the Arachnids.

912
01:07:46,802 --> 01:07:48,872
虫族经过三百代
When a colony reaches a certain size...

913
01:07:48,972 --> 01:07:51,672
进化一定会变聪明
300 generations or something, it gets smarter.

914
01:07:51,762 --> 01:07:53,142
- 聪明的虫子? - 快...
- Insects with intelligence? - Now, wait...

915
01:07:53,222 --> 01:07:54,962
你遇到过吗? 难以置信...
Have you ever met one? I can't believe...

916
01:07:55,062 --> 01:07:56,972
- 这种想法太荒谬了 - 请你听我说
- I am hearing this nonsense. - Would you just wait a moment?

917
01:07:57,062 --> 01:08:00,012
- 这是我听过的最荒谬讲话 - 可能 可能
- This is the most ridiculous conversation I have ever had. - Maybe... Maybe...

918
01:08:00,102 --> 01:08:03,802
也许有一种虫我们没见过
there is some kind of bug that we haven't seen yet.:

919
01:08:03,902 --> 01:08:06,312
领导阶级 虫族首脑
a leadership caste, a-a hive brain.

920
01:08:06,402 --> 01:08:11,062
虫族首脑? 虫子也会思考? 才怪...
Brain Bugs? Frankly, I find the idea of a bug that thinks offensive!

921
01:08:25,092 --> 01:08:28,752
星舰基地 杨罗杰号请求进入
Ticonderoga, this is Rodger Young requesting approach vector.

922
01:08:28,842 --> 01:08:30,672
收到 杨罗杰号
Affirmative, Rodger Young.

923
01:08:30,762 --> 01:08:33,552
座标l00951
One-zero-zero-niner-five-two.

924
01:08:33,642 --> 01:08:34,802
欢迎回来
Welcome back.

925
01:08:37,102 --> 01:08:38,432
我的天
My God.

926
01:08:40,352 --> 01:08:42,432
怎么会这样?
How could this happen?

927
01:08:42,522 --> 01:08:44,892
我们自以为比虫族聪明
We thought we were smarter than the bugs.

928
01:09:18,232 --> 01:09:20,902
"伤亡人数：308 563"

929
01:09:24,062 --> 01:09:26,642
很奇怪 几乎没有人被俘
It's strange. There's almost no wounded at all.

930
01:09:26,732 --> 01:09:28,772
虫族不抓俘虏
Bugs don't take prisoners.

931
01:09:35,192 --> 01:09:39,242
"强尼·瑞哥 阵亡"
哦...不...
Oh, no.

932
01:09:40,702 --> 01:09:42,032
看
Look.

933
01:09:46,542 --> 01:09:48,702
- 卡门... - 这里
- Carmen... - See it? Right there.

934
01:10:10,662 --> 01:10:13,422
- 他在那儿 - 我们会把他叫醒
- There he is. - Come on, we'll just wake him up.

935
01:10:13,502 --> 01:10:17,912
嘿 强尼
Hey,Johnny! Hey!

936
01:10:18,002 --> 01:10:20,922
- 瑞哥 - 强尼 醒醒
- Hey, Rico! - Hey,Johnny!

937
01:10:21,012 --> 01:10:22,922
- 瑞哥 醒醒 - 你好吗 小鱼儿?
- Hey, Rico!Wake up! - How you doin', fish boy?

938
01:10:23,012 --> 01:10:25,582
看 你死了
Hey, look. You're dead!

939
01:10:25,682 --> 01:10:27,972
你阵亡了
Killed in action!

940
01:10:30,352 --> 01:10:32,262
- 再过三天就能出来 - 三天
- Three more days. - Three days.

941
01:10:32,352 --> 01:10:34,342
- 你出局了 - 再见
- And you're out. - Good as new. See you later.

942
01:10:34,442 --> 01:10:35,772
回头见
Bye.

943
01:11:04,972 --> 01:11:06,712
新的部队怎么样?
So what do you hear about our new unit?

944
01:11:06,802 --> 01:11:09,212
硬汉部队消灭的大虫比谁都多
Roughnecks killed more bugs than any other outfit on Big K.

945
01:11:09,312 --> 01:11:12,142
听说中尉很严厉
Yeah, well, I hear their lieutenant's a real nutbuster.

946
01:11:15,152 --> 01:11:16,812
士官长是谁?
Who's top kick?

947
01:11:19,322 --> 01:11:20,982
你想当吗?
You want the job, huh?

948
01:11:21,072 --> 01:11:22,402
我不介意
I wouldn't mind.

949
01:11:22,492 --> 01:11:24,362
我很介意
I would.

950
01:11:25,822 --> 01:11:27,152
我只想出力
Just doing my part.

951
01:11:27,242 --> 01:11:28,702
命令
Orders.

952
01:11:31,332 --> 01:11:32,742
你的呢?
Yours?

953
01:11:32,832 --> 01:11:34,572
你还到哪里打过仗?
Where you been besides Big K?

954
01:11:34,662 --> 01:11:38,532
- 土星外环 西格玛海滩 - 西格玛海滩
- Outer rings, Zegema Beach. - Zegema Beach?

955
01:11:38,632 --> 01:11:41,002
- 我一直想去那儿 - 好运气
- I always wanted to go there. - Good luck.

956
01:11:41,092 --> 01:11:46,162
- 不用去了 那里不存在了 - 听说你们的中尉挺麻烦的
- It's not there any more. - So, I hear your lieutenant's a real nutbuster.

957
01:11:49,262 --> 01:11:52,012
别批评中尉 他救我一命
No one talks about the lieutenant that way.

958
01:11:52,102 --> 01:11:54,552
- 他救过我 - 也救过我
- He saved my life. - Mine too.

959
01:11:55,942 --> 01:11:57,812
- 我也是 - 还有我
- Same for me. - Me too.

960
01:11:59,612 --> 01:12:02,522
听起来他人很好
Well, sounds like he's quite a guy.

961
01:12:02,612 --> 01:12:04,272
你以为是谁救了你?
Who do you think saved your ass?

962
01:12:05,452 --> 01:12:08,902
待命 立正
Stand by. Attention on deck!

963
01:12:21,292 --> 01:12:23,372
新来的听好
This is for you new people.

964
01:12:23,462 --> 01:12:25,502
我只有一个规则
I only have one rule:

965
01:12:25,592 --> 01:12:28,962
全力以赴 不能退缩
Everyone fights. No one quits.

966
01:12:29,052 --> 01:12:32,052
明白吗?
You don't do your job, I'll shoot you.

967
01:12:32,142 --> 01:12:33,382
明白吗?
Do you get me?

968
01:12:33,472 --> 01:12:35,472
明白 长官
We get you, sir!

969
01:12:37,192 --> 01:12:39,592
- 欢迎到硬汉部队 - 瑞斯加科的硬汉
- Welcome to the Roughnecks. - Rasczak's Roughnecks!

970
01:12:40,862 --> 01:12:42,932
稍息 听好
At ease. Listen up.

971
01:12:43,022 --> 01:12:46,612
新的元帅有新的战略
We got a new Sky Marshal and a new battle plan.

972
01:12:46,702 --> 01:12:49,102
先一一消灭克兰达夫...
We're gonna clean out the systems outlying Klendathu...

973
01:12:49,202 --> 01:12:51,362
周围的星球
one planet at a time.

974
01:12:51,452 --> 01:12:53,612
明天攻击探戈幽灵星
Tomorrow we hit Tango Urilla.

975
01:12:53,702 --> 01:12:58,112
先进行轰炸然后再消灭残留的敌人
After Fleet glasses the planet, MI mops up.

976
01:12:58,212 --> 01:12:59,452
继续吧
Carry on.

977
01:13:49,722 --> 01:13:52,292
好吧 分散开来
All right. Spread out!

978
01:13:52,392 --> 01:13:56,052
核弹小组 找到虫穴就炸掉
Fire teams! You locate a bug hole, nuke it.

979
01:14:03,902 --> 01:14:05,812
华肯 带上弗洛斯和瑞哥
Watkins, shake out Flores and Rico.

980
01:14:05,902 --> 01:14:08,222
收到 走吧
Copy that. Move out!

981
01:14:08,322 --> 01:14:11,152
第一排 我们到山谷
First platoon, we're going for that ridge.

982
01:14:11,242 --> 01:14:14,162
- 利维 跟我来 - 我要跟着瑞哥
- Levy, you're with me. - No, I'm in A Squad. I'm going with Rico.

983
01:14:14,242 --> 01:14:15,742
给我闭嘴
Shut up and follow me!

984
01:14:54,162 --> 01:14:55,982
你喜欢那个?
Hey, you like that?

985
01:14:56,072 --> 01:14:58,072
吃屎的大臭虫
Fungus-sucking sack of maggot puke!

986
01:14:58,162 --> 01:14:59,742
华肯 它死了
It's dead, Watkins! It's dead!

987
01:15:04,872 --> 01:15:07,122
死了就没什么可怕的
Ain't much to look at after you scrape them off your boot.

988
01:15:08,672 --> 01:15:11,422
发现虫穴 那儿
Bug hole. There.

989
01:15:26,192 --> 01:15:27,352
炸掉它 瑞哥
Nuke 'em, Rico!

990
01:15:33,362 --> 01:15:34,822
准备射击
Fire in the hole!

991
01:15:46,542 --> 01:15:48,952
我们受到攻击 快来支援
Watkins, we're under heavy attack. Position M-4.

992
01:15:49,042 --> 01:15:51,292
- 快去! - 快!
- Get over here! - Move!

993
01:16:01,392 --> 01:16:04,392
- 你需要除虫吗 小姐? - 闭嘴 大兵
- You got a bug problem, ma'am? - Ah, stow it, trooper!

994
01:16:25,962 --> 01:16:28,032
大甲虫
Tanker!

995
01:16:28,122 --> 01:16:31,212
- 妈的! - 快走吧
- Oh, shit! - Come on! Move!

996
01:16:39,932 --> 01:16:41,842
趴下来
Get down!

997
01:16:49,982 --> 01:16:51,182
跟我来
Come on!

998
01:17:59,512 --> 01:18:01,582
通知救援队
Stay down, sucker!

999
01:18:03,682 --> 01:18:05,262
呼叫检索
Call for retrieval.

1000
01:18:05,352 --> 01:18:08,432
- 医官 - 好身手
- Medic! - Nice moves.

1001
01:18:08,522 --> 01:18:10,762
你在哪儿学来的?
Where'd you learn how to do that, soldier?

1002
01:18:10,852 --> 01:18:13,942
学校里 你不记得吗?
Back in school, sir. Don't you remember?

1003
01:18:14,022 --> 01:18:18,022
- 我是球队队长 - 瑞哥
- I was captain of the team. - Rico?

1004
01:18:18,112 --> 01:18:20,862
- 长官 - 我需要一名下士
- Sir. - I need a corporal.

1005
01:18:20,952 --> 01:18:24,532
在你阵亡之前你就当下士
You're it until you're dead or till I find somebody better.

1006
01:18:25,452 --> 01:18:27,442
谢谢你 长官
Thank you, sir.

1007
01:18:27,542 --> 01:18:30,212
- 好了 结束了 - 干得好 下士
- All right, saddle up! Show's over. - Way to go, Corporal.

1008
01:18:30,292 --> 01:18:35,632
- 我要一名班长 - 不行 找搞砸过
- Hey, I need a squad leader. - Oh, no. No, I've been there and blew it.

1009
01:18:35,712 --> 01:18:37,122
我只想杀敌
I'm just here to fight.

1010
01:18:38,422 --> 01:18:40,582
你呢?
What about it, Diz?

1011
01:18:40,672 --> 01:18:44,632
看来就是我了
First sergeant, get your gear in section...Looks like I'm your girl, sir.

1012
01:18:49,562 --> 01:18:51,182
- 待会儿见 - 好
- Catch you later. - All right.

1013
01:18:57,192 --> 01:18:59,062
听好
Listen up!

1014
01:18:59,152 --> 01:19:02,352
最好的士兵要有最好的享受
I expect the best, and I give the best!

1015
01:19:06,202 --> 01:19:07,532
这是啤酒
Here's the beer!

1016
01:19:11,582 --> 01:19:13,542
这是娱乐的东西
Here's the entertainment!

1017
01:19:18,042 --> 01:19:20,042
玩得开心点 这是命今
Have fun! That's an order!

1018
01:19:21,132 --> 01:19:22,712
这是我的
This one's for me!

1019
01:19:24,132 --> 01:19:25,712
谢了 中尉
Thank you, Lieutenant!

1020
01:19:29,432 --> 01:19:30,762
瑞哥
Rico!

1021
01:19:32,232 --> 01:19:34,302
你很会除虫
You kill bugs good.

1022
01:19:34,392 --> 01:19:35,722
谢了
Thanks.

1023
01:19:37,562 --> 01:19:39,892
你在战前认识中尉了吧
You knew the lieutenant before the war.

1024
01:19:39,982 --> 01:19:41,892
他为人如何?
What was he like?

1025
01:19:41,992 --> 01:19:45,072
他是个老师 什么都懂
He was a teacher. Kind of like he knew it all.

1026
01:19:45,162 --> 01:19:47,232
总是带着微笑
He always had this little smile.

1027
01:19:47,322 --> 01:19:50,742
现在他可笑不出来
Yeah, well, he don't smile much any more.

1028
01:19:50,832 --> 01:19:54,582
死这么多人怎么笑得出来
Yeah, well, I guess your bottle fills up real quick when your kids get smeared.

1029
01:19:54,662 --> 01:19:57,122
- 来吧 下士 - 我不跳舞了
- Come on, Corporal. - Ah, nah, I don't do that any more.

1030
01:19:57,212 --> 01:19:59,702
我记得你以前跳 来嘛
I remember when you used to dance. Come on.

1031
01:19:59,792 --> 01:20:01,212
我得下令吗?
Do I have to pull rank?

1032
01:20:04,012 --> 01:20:05,552
抱歉 长官
Excuse me, sir.

1033
01:20:14,352 --> 01:20:19,432
瑞哥 你问过我的意见 想听吗?
Rico. You once asked me for advice. Want some now?

1034
01:20:19,522 --> 01:20:22,232
- 想 长官 - 中尉 总部来电
- Yes, sir. - Lieutenant, HQ is on the com.

1035
01:20:24,692 --> 01:20:26,732
看到好机会就要把握
Never pass up a good thing.

1036
01:20:35,712 --> 01:20:38,332
华肯 喝啤酒吗?
Watkins. Beer?

1037
01:21:00,862 --> 01:21:03,432
瑞哥 跳完舞你打算干嘛?
So, Rico, what are you doing after the dance?

1038
01:21:51,072 --> 01:21:52,452
有什么好笑?
What's so funny?

1039
01:21:53,992 --> 01:21:56,152
世事真是难以预料
You know, just the way things work out.

1040
01:22:13,682 --> 01:22:16,172
我们终于在一起
We finally got together, Diz.

1041
01:22:19,352 --> 01:22:20,852
我爱你 强尼
I love you,Johnny.

1042
01:22:31,452 --> 01:22:32,692
瑞哥
Rico!

1043
01:22:35,452 --> 01:22:38,292
准备出动 欧文将军在P星遇难
We're moving out. There's been a distress call from General Owen on Planet P.

1044
01:22:38,372 --> 01:22:40,532
穿好军服 十分钟后报到
So get your shit wired and report in ten minutes.

1045
01:22:40,622 --> 01:22:42,032
是的
Yes, sir.

1046
01:22:42,122 --> 01:22:43,622
谁在那里?
Who's that with you?

1047
01:22:47,212 --> 01:22:49,292
弗洛斯 长官
Flores, sir.

1048
01:22:50,472 --> 01:22:52,542
二十分钟吧
Make it 20 minutes.

1049
01:22:52,632 --> 01:22:53,802
是的 长官
Yes, sir.

1050
01:22:55,052 --> 01:22:56,382
二十分钟?
Twenty minutes?

1051
01:22:57,562 --> 01:22:58,882
应该来得及
We can do it.

1052
01:23:37,262 --> 01:23:38,922
威士忌哨站 收到吗?
Whiskey Outpost, do you copy?

1053
01:23:39,012 --> 01:23:42,052
这是硬汉部队201 请回答
This is Roughneck 2-0 on tac three. Come in, please.

1054
01:23:43,352 --> 01:23:44,762
威士忌哨站 威士忌哨站
Whiskey Outpost, Whiskey Outpost,

1055
01:23:44,852 --> 01:23:47,102
这是硬汉部队201
this is Roughneck 2-0 on tac three.

1056
01:23:47,192 --> 01:23:49,432
- 将军有消息吗? - 没有 长官
- Any contact with General Owen? - No, sir.

1057
01:23:49,522 --> 01:23:50,942
连发送讯号都没有
Not even the transponder signal.

1058
01:23:51,032 --> 01:23:54,442
被山谷挡住 到高处去
It's these canyons. Go to higher ground, Sergeant.

1059
01:24:00,412 --> 01:24:02,282
威士忌哨站
Whiskey Outpost, Whiskey Outpost...

1060
01:24:02,372 --> 01:24:04,202
这是硬汉部队
this is Roughneck 2-0 on...

1061
01:24:16,302 --> 01:24:17,932
把你的枪给我
Sugar, your weapon.

1062
01:24:24,732 --> 01:24:26,932
救救我
Help me! Help me!

1063
01:24:37,242 --> 01:24:40,822
如果我落入敌手 你们也要杀了我
I'd expect anyone in this unit to do the same for me.

1064
01:24:42,202 --> 01:24:43,952
- 瑞哥 - 长官
- Rico. - Sir.

1065
01:24:44,042 --> 01:24:46,032
你是代理士官长 带队
You're acting sergeant. Move 'em out.

1066
01:24:47,422 --> 01:24:50,292
你们听到了 快走吧
You heard the lieutenant! Saddle up!

1067
01:25:42,102 --> 01:25:45,462
天哪 有人血洗这地方
Jeez, someone really humped the bunk.

1068
01:25:45,562 --> 01:25:47,762
- 华肯 - 长官
- Watkins. - Sir.

1069
01:25:47,852 --> 01:25:50,182
检查哨站 检查死尸
Secure this compound. Police these bodies.

1070
01:25:50,272 --> 01:25:53,442
是的 长官 三个人上塔架 快点
Yes, sir. Give me three up on the tower, now!

1071
01:25:53,522 --> 01:25:55,482
这里和那里建立监视哨
Aye-aye.OP there! OP there!

1072
01:25:55,572 --> 01:25:58,242
检查死尸
Away! Number Two, police up these bodies!

1073
01:25:58,322 --> 01:26:00,282
里头好臭
Stinks in there.Second squad, come with me on the gate!

1074
01:26:00,362 --> 01:26:02,612
- 瑞哥 - 是的 长官
- Rico! - Churchill, come with me! - Yes, sir.

1075
01:26:02,702 --> 01:26:04,282
我们需要救援 这地方都是大虫
We need retrieval. This place crawls.

1076
01:26:04,372 --> 01:26:06,612
再找人修好通讯连线
Get somebody in the communications tent and get me an uplink.

1077
01:26:06,702 --> 01:26:08,582
是的 长官 蒂丝 去吧
Yes, sir. Diz, check it out.

1078
01:26:08,662 --> 01:26:10,072
- 知道了 - 指挥小组跟我来
- Roger. - Command group with me.

1079
01:26:14,712 --> 01:26:15,962
天哪
Ah, shit.

1080
01:26:16,052 --> 01:26:17,422
中尉
Lieutenant!

1081
01:26:19,882 --> 01:26:23,092
他们吃饭时遭到大虫偷袭
Dirty bugs came in right while they were having chow.

1082
01:26:28,732 --> 01:26:31,602
它们从这里进来
Yeah, this is where they got in.

1083
01:26:33,232 --> 01:26:35,472
中尉
Lieutenant.

1084
01:26:35,572 --> 01:26:38,272
你最好来看看
I think you're gonna want to see this.

1085
01:26:38,362 --> 01:26:39,942
什么事 弗洛斯?
What do you got, Flores?

1086
01:26:40,032 --> 01:26:41,862
这地方真可怕
God, I hate this place.

1087
01:26:56,882 --> 01:26:59,332
你觉得这是什么? 瑞哥?
What does that look like to you, Rico?

1088
01:27:02,052 --> 01:27:03,882
看来虫钻进他大脑
Looks like a bug was in his brain, sir.

1089
01:27:13,732 --> 01:27:16,302
它们吸光他大脑
They sucked his brains out.

1090
01:27:25,742 --> 01:27:27,072
打开来
Open that.

1091
01:27:30,582 --> 01:27:32,412
立正
Officer on the deck!

1092
01:27:32,502 --> 01:27:34,992
- 把将军扶起来 - 走了?
- Pick up the general. - Gone?

1093
01:27:35,082 --> 01:27:36,662
安全吗? 我们得快走
Is it safe? We've got to get out of here!

1094
01:27:36,752 --> 01:27:38,992
- 将军 长官 - 我们...
- General!, Sir! - We've gotta...

1095
01:27:42,422 --> 01:27:46,262
谢谢你 谢谢你们
Thank God for you, all of you.

1096
01:27:46,342 --> 01:27:49,592
你们都是英雄 你们全都是
You're all gonna be heroes. Every last one of you.

1097
01:27:49,682 --> 01:27:52,172
- 把洞穴封起来 - 好的
- Close that hole. - Yes, sir.

1098
01:27:52,272 --> 01:27:55,432
我得逃命 联邦秘密太重要
I had to evade capture. The security of the Federation was at stake.

1099
01:27:59,362 --> 01:28:02,112
我知道这地区的攻击战略
I have operational knowledge of what we're up to out here.

1100
01:28:02,192 --> 01:28:04,602
- 赶快连线 - 我正在努力
- Flores, I need that uplink. - Working on it, sir.

1101
01:28:04,702 --> 01:28:06,692
你看
Damn it.See?

1102
01:28:06,782 --> 01:28:08,442
它们钻进你的大脑
They get in your mind.Battlegroup, this is Roughneck 2-0.

1103
01:28:08,532 --> 01:28:10,112
- 你看法利的下场 - 你知道吗?
- Look, they did it to Farley. - Do you read?

1104
01:28:10,202 --> 01:28:12,282
它们钻进你的大脑 逼你做事情
They got in his mind.Come in, Battlegroup. This is Roughneck 2-0.

1105
01:28:12,372 --> 01:28:15,462
它们逼法利联络指挥部
They make you do things. They made Farley call headquarters.

1106
01:28:15,542 --> 01:28:17,282
求救讯号是个圈套
The distress call was a trap.

1107
01:28:17,382 --> 01:28:20,742
它们也想知道我们的底细
They're just like us. They want to know what makes us tick.

1108
01:28:20,842 --> 01:28:22,792
摸清我们的弱点 这样才能消灭我们
They want to know us, so they can kill us.

1109
01:28:22,882 --> 01:28:24,792
敌人会来袭 准备迎战
Roughnecks, this is lead. Prepare for attack.

1110
01:28:24,882 --> 01:28:27,212
- 我们会被攻击 - 救援机在哪呢?
- I repeat, we're gonna be attacked. - Where's the retrieval boat?

1111
01:28:27,302 --> 01:28:30,222
紧急状况这是硬汉部队 收到吗?
Mayday. Mayday. This is Roughneck 2-0 to Battlegroup. Do you read?

1112
01:28:30,312 --> 01:28:32,132
哦 天哪
Oh, God!

1113
01:28:32,222 --> 01:28:35,142
天哪 我们死定了 懂吗?
We're gonna die! Don't you understand?

1114
01:28:35,232 --> 01:28:36,562
我们都要死了
We're all gonna die!

1115
01:28:38,152 --> 01:28:39,562
第二阵容 跟我来!
Second squad, follow me!

1116
01:28:39,652 --> 01:28:42,602
- 克制一下自己 将军 - 不行
- Control yourself, General. - I can't.

1117
01:28:42,692 --> 01:28:44,232
我不行 我做不到
I can't.

1118
01:28:44,322 --> 01:28:45,942
你干脆杀死我
I wish you'd just shoot me.

1119
01:28:48,322 --> 01:28:51,742
中尉 他的脑袋不清楚
Lieutenant! He's just a little out of his mind, sir.

1120
01:28:52,992 --> 01:28:54,902
大虫
Bugs! Bugs!

1121
01:28:55,002 --> 01:28:57,242
好吧
Die! All right.

1122
01:28:57,332 --> 01:29:00,252
准备好 全力开火
Warm it all up! Everything you've got!

1123
01:29:00,342 --> 01:29:02,412
- 快 - 大兵们 拚命吧
- Move! - Come on, you apes!

1124
01:29:02,502 --> 01:29:04,082
你们想一直活着吧?
You want to live forever?

1125
01:29:06,382 --> 01:29:07,762
- 这儿! - 我得到了虫子!
- Here! - I got bugs!

1126
01:29:38,162 --> 01:29:39,492
开火吧
Fire at will!

1127
01:30:19,912 --> 01:30:21,332
飞虫来袭
Incoming!

1128
01:30:53,372 --> 01:30:55,572
瑞哥 连线好了吗?
Rico, where's my communication?

1129
01:30:55,662 --> 01:30:57,742
- 蒂丝 连线呢? - 再等一分钟
- Diz, status on the uplink! - Give me a minute.

1130
01:30:57,832 --> 01:30:59,702
我们没有一分钟了
We don't have a minute!

1131
01:31:09,012 --> 01:31:11,082
舰队 这是硬汉部队
Battlegroup, this is Roughneck 2-0. We are under...

1132
01:31:11,172 --> 01:31:14,262
- 这里是杨罗杰号 请说 - 我们受袭 请来救援
- This is Rodger Young. Go ahead. - We are under attack, sir. We need retrieval now!

1133
01:31:14,342 --> 01:31:15,762
P星球没敌人
We have Planet Pas clear.

1134
01:31:15,852 --> 01:31:17,922
到处都是 快来接人
This place crawls, sir. We need pickup now!

1135
01:31:18,012 --> 01:31:20,262
- 说出位置 - 追踪无线电讯号
- What's your position? - Come down on this transmission.

1136
01:31:20,352 --> 01:31:21,932
哨站? 太疯狂了
Inside the outpost? That's crazy!

1137
01:31:22,022 --> 01:31:23,892
希望飞行员也疯狂 完毕
Well, I hope you have a crazy pilot. Out!

1138
01:31:56,472 --> 01:31:58,092
中尉
Lieutenant!

1139
01:31:58,182 --> 01:31:59,762
救援机正赶来
Boat coming down, sir!

1140
01:31:59,852 --> 01:32:03,352
退进去 快撤
Fall back into the compound! Fall back!

1141
01:32:28,042 --> 01:32:30,712
全力抵挡敌人
Hold here! Hold what you've got!

1142
01:32:41,392 --> 01:32:42,722
弹药快没了
Running low!

1143
01:32:44,062 --> 01:32:45,472
我没了
I'm out!

1144
01:32:45,562 --> 01:32:47,802
拿去 省着点
Here! Make 'em count!

1145
01:33:07,252 --> 01:33:09,162
掩护救援机 撤
Make cover fire! Fall back!

1146
01:33:25,272 --> 01:33:27,012
快 快 快
Move, move, move!

1147
01:33:29,442 --> 01:33:31,932
快登机 撤
Fall back to the boat! Haul ass!

1148
01:33:45,662 --> 01:33:47,702
- 我的天 - 哦
- Oh, my God! - Oh!

1149
01:33:51,382 --> 01:33:53,952
- 把他拉上来 - 快
- Get him outta there! Pull! - Come on!

1150
01:34:00,142 --> 01:34:02,262
瑞哥 瑞哥
Rico! Rico!

1151
01:34:03,642 --> 01:34:06,892
- 你知道该怎么做 - 是的 长官
- You know what to do! - Yes, sir!

1152
01:34:11,652 --> 01:34:13,222
快下手 瑞哥
Do it, Rico!

1153
01:34:38,512 --> 01:34:41,082
- 嗯! - 蒂丝!
- Yeah! - Dizzy!

1154
01:35:02,952 --> 01:35:04,692
不!
No!

1155
01:35:04,782 --> 01:35:07,572
王牌 帮我拉住她
Ace, help me! Hold her down!

1156
01:35:12,542 --> 01:35:14,702
把她抬上机
Move! Get her into the boat!

1157
01:35:16,292 --> 01:35:18,092
蒂丝 千万别死
Come on, Diz! Don't die on me!

1158
01:35:18,172 --> 01:35:19,452
把她抬走 快
Let's get her out! Let's go, let's go!

1159
01:35:25,892 --> 01:35:27,602
快上去
Let's go! Get aboard!

1160
01:35:29,222 --> 01:35:31,102
你们 快点...
Tower, let's go!

1161
01:35:37,232 --> 01:35:41,152
快来吧
Let's move it, tower! Run!

1162
01:35:47,202 --> 01:35:48,582
升空
Lift off!

1163
01:36:19,192 --> 01:36:23,652
- 强尼 我快死了 - 不
- Johnny, I'm dying-dying. - No.

1164
01:36:23,742 --> 01:36:25,902
不 你不会有事的 蒂丝
You're gonna be all right, Diz.

1165
01:36:25,992 --> 01:36:29,162
没关系
It's all right...

1166
01:36:29,242 --> 01:36:31,702
因为我爱过你
because I got to have you.

1167
01:36:39,172 --> 01:36:41,212
别放开我
Johnny, don't let me go!

1168
01:36:41,302 --> 01:36:43,042
强...强...
Joh...Joh...

1169
01:36:43,132 --> 01:36:45,122
别放开...别放开...
Don't let... Don't let...

1170
01:37:09,702 --> 01:37:11,412
我要你知道
I think you should know...

1171
01:37:12,662 --> 01:37:14,952
你的朋友瑞哥在后面
your friend Rico is back there.

1172
01:37:24,212 --> 01:37:27,962
快通知舰队轰炸这星球
Get on the com and tell Fleet to glass that rock.

1173
01:37:28,052 --> 01:37:29,762
谁下的命令 下士?
On whose authority, Corporal?

1174
01:37:29,842 --> 01:37:32,932
我的命令 任务由我指挥
That would be mine, sir. I assumed command of the mission.

1175
01:37:34,352 --> 01:37:36,802
杨罗杰号 我正式代表
Rodger Young, we have an official request...

1176
01:37:36,892 --> 01:37:40,012
机动部队要求轰炸P星球
by the Mobile Infantry to commence bombardment of Planet P.

1177
01:37:41,362 --> 01:37:43,762
我以为你死了
I thought you were dead.

1178
01:37:43,862 --> 01:37:46,942
我没死 很多战友都死了
I'm not, but a lot of my troopers are.

1179
01:37:47,032 --> 01:37:48,992
不行
Negative on your request, DeRuyter.

1180
01:37:49,072 --> 01:37:51,282
元帅另有安排
The Sky Marshal has other plans for Planet P.

1181
01:37:51,372 --> 01:37:52,612
欢迎回来
Welcome back.

1182
01:37:52,702 --> 01:37:55,792
机动部队负责死 舰队负责飞
MI does the dying. Fleet just does the flying.

1183
01:37:55,872 --> 01:37:57,782
等等 有动静了
Hold on. Something's up.

1184
01:37:57,872 --> 01:38:00,362
舰队要进行大规模行动
Fleet's mobilized for a big operation.

1185
01:38:29,182 --> 01:38:31,002
立正
Attention on deck!

1186
01:38:38,102 --> 01:38:40,012
有人曾问我...
Once somebody asked me...

1187
01:38:40,102 --> 01:38:42,512
公民和平民...
if I knew the difference between a citizen...

1188
01:38:42,612 --> 01:38:44,522
有何不同
and a civilian.

1189
01:38:44,612 --> 01:38:46,192
我现在知道了
I can tell you now.

1190
01:38:46,282 --> 01:38:48,352
公民有...
A citizen has the courage...

1191
01:38:48,452 --> 01:38:52,942
捍卫人类安全的勇气
to make the safety of the human race their personal responsibility.

1192
01:38:57,122 --> 01:38:59,532
蒂丝是我朋友
Dizzy was my friend.

1193
01:38:59,622 --> 01:39:01,752
她也是战士
She was a soldier.

1194
01:39:01,832 --> 01:39:03,712
更重要的是
But more than that...

1195
01:39:03,792 --> 01:39:06,202
她是联邦公民
she was a citizen of the Federation.

1196
01:39:08,632 --> 01:39:10,542
敬礼
Present arms!

1197
01:39:29,072 --> 01:39:31,862
放下
Order arms!

1198
01:39:35,242 --> 01:39:36,992
向左转
Left face!

1199
01:39:51,092 --> 01:39:53,172
- 立正 - 继续
- Officer on deck! - Carry on.

1200
01:39:54,762 --> 01:39:57,472
治葬队伍解散
Burial detail dismissed.

1201
01:40:04,442 --> 01:40:06,682
稍息
At ease.

1202
01:40:06,772 --> 01:40:10,022
- 你好吗 卡尔? - 我很好 卡门
- How are you, Carl? - Carmen, good.

1203
01:40:10,112 --> 01:40:13,032
强尼 我很遗憾你们被派到P星球
Johnny, I'm sorry it had to be your unit on P.

1204
01:40:13,112 --> 01:40:15,572
那次任务的生还率很低
That mission had a very low survival probability.

1205
01:40:15,662 --> 01:40:17,702
虫族设下圈套 对吧?
The bugs laid a trap for us, didn't they?

1206
01:40:19,122 --> 01:40:21,532
证明它们有智慧
Elegant proof of intelligence, isn't it?

1207
01:40:21,622 --> 01:40:24,082
我早就猜到P星球上有虫族首脑
We thought there might be a Brain Bug on P.

1208
01:40:24,172 --> 01:40:26,082
你早就知道却派他们下去?
You knew, and you sent them anyway?

1209
01:40:26,172 --> 01:40:29,542
我们找不到首脑就不能进行攻击
We couldn't afford to launch an operation if there wasn't one.

1210
01:40:31,462 --> 01:40:34,882
你不苟同 很遗憾
You don't approve. Well, too bad.

1211
01:40:34,972 --> 01:40:36,882
事关人类存亡
We're in this for the species, boys and girls.

1212
01:40:36,972 --> 01:40:39,342
它们数量众多
It's simple numbers. They have more.

1213
01:40:39,432 --> 01:40:41,172
我每天都得决定...
And every day I have to make decisions...

1214
01:40:41,272 --> 01:40:44,102
派你这种人去送死
that send hundreds of people like you to their deaths.

1215
01:40:44,192 --> 01:40:46,562
难道你不知道吗 中校?
Didn't they tell you, Colonel?

1216
01:40:46,652 --> 01:40:48,972
机动部队专门送死
That's what the Mobile Infantry is good for.

1217
01:40:49,072 --> 01:40:51,852
希望你还能再战
I hope you're ready for more.

1218
01:40:51,942 --> 01:40:55,232
我们要回去活抓首脑
We're going back to P to capture that Brain.

1219
01:40:57,282 --> 01:41:00,032
硬汉部队随时备战
The Roughnecks are always ready, sir.

1220
01:41:00,122 --> 01:41:02,742
他们需要一名中尉 想当吗?
I hear they need a new lieutenant. Want the job?

1221
01:41:02,832 --> 01:41:06,832
好的 等我阵亡你再换人
I'll take it, till I get killed or you find someone better.

1222
01:41:09,042 --> 01:41:12,212
全体人员报到
Attention. All personnel report to your stations.

1223
01:41:12,302 --> 01:41:15,712
75分钟后降落
- Well... - Prepare for drop in 7 5 minutes.

1224
01:41:15,802 --> 01:41:17,592
你要小心 强尼
Take care of yourself,Johnny.

1225
01:41:17,682 --> 01:41:19,472
后会有期
I'll see you again.

1226
01:41:32,652 --> 01:41:34,312
立正
Officer on deck!

1227
01:41:51,752 --> 01:41:55,342
- 这些孩子是谁? - 支援部队
- Who are all these kids? - We got reinforced.

1228
01:41:55,422 --> 01:41:57,632
多半是菜鸟
Most of them are fresh out of boot.

1229
01:41:57,722 --> 01:41:59,542
我们算是老兵
We're the old men, Ace.

1230
01:42:01,932 --> 01:42:04,172
新兵听好
This is for all you new people.

1231
01:42:04,272 --> 01:42:06,512
我只有一个规则
I only have one rule:

1232
01:42:06,602 --> 01:42:09,692
全力以赴 不能退缩
Everyone fights. No one quits.

1233
01:42:09,772 --> 01:42:12,862
不尽力我就亲自宰了你
If you don't do your job, I'll kill you myself.

1234
01:42:12,942 --> 01:42:14,222
明白吗?
Do you get me?

1235
01:42:14,322 --> 01:42:16,362
明白 长官
We get you, sir!

1236
01:42:16,442 --> 01:42:21,112
- 欢迎加入硬汉部队 - 瑞哥的硬汉部队
- Welcome to the Roughnecks. - Rico's Roughnecks!

1237
01:42:23,742 --> 01:42:26,322
今天要进入虫穴
Today we're gonna pay a visit to Bug City.

1238
01:42:26,412 --> 01:42:29,702
找一只没见过的大虫
We're lookin' for a bug no one's ever seen before.

1239
01:42:29,792 --> 01:42:31,622
一只聪明的虫子
Some kind of smart bug.

1240
01:42:37,552 --> 01:42:39,512
它可能知道我们要去 来吧
And it probably knows we're comin'.

1241
01:42:43,602 --> 01:42:45,472
快! 跑 跑 跑
Come on! Run, run, run, run, run!

1242
01:42:56,942 --> 01:42:58,902
快闪躲
